  "contents": "<div class=\"content markitup-box\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t我先说清楚，我求的这是中国的国运签不是中共的党运签，二者不可混为一谈。<br/>\n<br/>\r\n因为中国大陆不像台湾那样有宫庙会去抽国运签，所以我就去台湾的命理网站上给中国大陆抽了个国运签。我抽到了第十四丙寅签。<br/>\n<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvZWQwMGEwNjQwNDJlZGEwY2UyZWQzLnBuZz93aWR0aD0xNjU5JmhlaWdodD05MTQ\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/ed00a064042eda0ce2ed3.png?width=1659&amp;height=914\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/ed00a064042eda0ce2ed3.png?width=1659&amp;height=914\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/ed00a064042eda0ce2ed3.png?width=1659&amp;height=914\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvZGM5NTA2MjU5MGM5YmU4NjE1M2U2LnBuZz93aWR0aD05MjUmaGVpZ2h0PTkxNA\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/dc95062590c9be86153e6.png?width=925&amp;height=914\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/dc95062590c9be86153e6.png?width=925&amp;height=914\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/dc95062590c9be86153e6.png?width=925&amp;height=914\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<br/>\n<br/>\r\n签诗后两句是关键，宽心且看月中桂，郎君即便见太平，这说明中共将亡，太平盛世即将到来。\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>",
